title: making a ranked team! aiming for gold
body: we have a bot lane, we need a good mid with a big champ pool. we also need a top laner who can play smart and tell us his tp timers. we need an active jungler who know how to jungle efficiently.

replies.body: Plat 4 top lane main with decent champ pool. IGN: YoshixZeFabulous
I main mid with a huge champion pool. Add me ingame Scrambles senpai
